Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:02.99,Part,screen,0,0,0,,Part Two
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.91,0:00:11.33,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,Yes, yes, hello there, Araragi-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.91,0:00:11.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はいはいこんにちはですよ 阿良々木先輩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.33,0:00:12.79,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,This is Ougi Oshino.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.33,0:00:12.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,忍野扇です
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.79,0:00:16.34,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,Now today, we will be studying \Nabout constellations.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.79,0:00:16.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,では今日は 星座についてのお勉強をしましょうね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.54,0:00:20.55,Default - Italics,Koyomi,0,0,0,,I realized right away \Nthat this was a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.54,0:00:20.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すぐにこれは夢なのだと気付いた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.76,0:00:28.97,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,For Araragi-senpai, who lives in Japan, the \Nconstellations in the southern skies may be difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.76,0:00:28.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,日本住まいの阿良々木先輩からすれば\N南天の星座は厳しいでしょうね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.22,0:00:36.62,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,Though my rival, Hanekawa-senpai, may perhaps \Nbe looking at them now from around Australia.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.22,0:00:36.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私のライバルである羽川先輩は\Nひょっとしたら今頃オーストラリアあたりでご覧になっているかもしれませんが
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.62,0:00:37.82,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,No, but really,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.62,0:00:37.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや本当
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.82,0:00:42.61,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,the southern hemisphere has many unfamiliar \Nconstellations, so it is amusing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.82,0:00:42.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,南半球には馴染みのない星座がたくさんありますから\N面白いものですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.86,0:00:45.53,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,There is Chameleon over that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.86,0:00:45.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あちらにはカメレオン座とかありますからね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.82,0:00:48.11,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,There's also Pictor (easel) and Vela (sail).
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.82,0:00:48.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あとは画架(がか)座とか 帆(ほ)座とか
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.11,0:00:50.74,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,There's even a constellation \Ncalled Hydrus (water snake).
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.11,0:00:50.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,水蛇(みずへび)座 というのもありますねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.74,0:00:51.75,Default Mid Low Cen,screen,0,0,0,,Water Snake
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.75,0:00:52.75,Default Mid Low Cen,screen,0,0,0,,Snake—with a "water" radical
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.91,0:00:55.75,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,I guess it's what we would call \Nthe Hydra (sea snake).
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.91,0:00:55.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こちらで言うところの海蛇座でしょうかね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.58,0:00:58.88,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,Surely you know of this one, the Hydra?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.58,0:00:58.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これはご存知ですよね 海蛇座
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.92,0:01:03.34,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,It's the biggest of the 88 constellations.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.92,0:01:03.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,八十八の星座の中で 最大の星座です
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.55,0:01:08.97,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,Though, it's difficult to determine how the \Nsize of a constellation is measured.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.55,0:01:08.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ま 星座の大きさをどういう風に計るかというのも\N難しいところですけれどね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.43,0:01:14.73,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,When you think of it three-dimensionally, \Nit pretty much falls apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.43,0:01:14.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,立体的に捉えると 割とバラけちゃいますし
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.73,0:01:17.23,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,However, the presence \Nthat this Hydra has...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.73,0:01:17.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただ 海蛇座のこの存在感は
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.61,0:01:23.28,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,...reminds one of Kiss-shot \NAcerola-orion Heart-under-blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.61,0:01:23.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,キスショット・アセロラオリオン・ハートアンダーブレードを\N連想させますよね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.03,0:01:28.32,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,They call the creature \Nin Hydra a "sea snake",
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.03,0:01:28.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そもそも海蛇座 海蛇とは言いますが
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.32,0:01:31.79,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,but it actually points to \Nthe legendary hydras.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.32,0:01:31.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これは伝説上 ヒドラのことを示しているのです
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.24,0:01:33.95,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,Do you know what a hydra is?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.24,0:01:33.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わかりますか? ヒドラ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.95,0:01:36.04,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,It's not an exaggeration \Nto say it's immortal.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.95,0:01:36.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,不死身と言っても過言ではない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.04,0:01:38.83,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,It's a monster that keeps regenerating \Nno matter how much you cut off.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.04,0:01:38.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,斬っても斬っても再生する怪物です
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.50,0:01:45.55,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,The one that defeats that hydra is \Nthe famous, courageous Heracles.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.50,0:01:45.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのヒドラを退治するのは\N有名な 勇猛な ヘラクレスなのですが
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.30,0:01:52.68,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,You probably cannot defeat Kiss-shot \NAcerola-orion Heart-under-blade with this method,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.30,0:01:52.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このやりかたでは\Nキスショット・アセロラオリオン・ハートアンダーブレードは倒せないでしょうが
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.60,0:01:56.39,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,but he chopped the nine heads \Nof the hydra one by one,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.60,0:01:56.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ヒドラの九つある首を順に斬り
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.39,0:02:00.27,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,and burnt the cut sections shut with a \Nflame to prevent them from regenerating.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.39,0:02:00.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,切り口を炎で焼いて塞(ふさ)ぎ\N再生できないようにしたのです
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.61,0:02:06.78,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,As a side note, during this fight \Nbetween Heracles and the hydra,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.61,0:02:06.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,余談ですが この海蛇とヘラクレスとの戦いの際
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.78,0:02:11.62,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,the crab from Cancer sided with the \Nhydra and attacked Heracles.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.78,0:02:11.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,海蛇の味方をしてヘラクレスを攻撃したのが\N蟹座の蟹なのです
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.24,0:02:15.79,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,It used its big claws you know \Nof to cut at Heracles.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.24,0:02:15.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,例の大きな鋏(はさみ)で\Nヘラクレスに切りつけました
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.50,0:02:19.17,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,Its attitude of challenging a giant \Nenemy with a small weapon is,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.50,0:02:19.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,小さな武器で大きな敵に挑む姿勢は
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.17,0:02:22.29,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,in fact, Senjougahara-senpai herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.17,0:02:22.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まさしく戦場ヶ原先輩そのものですね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.71,0:02:26.29,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,When you awaken, please tell \NSenjougahara-senpai about this episode,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.71,0:02:26.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,目が覚めたらこの辺りのエピソードを戦場ヶ原先輩に話して
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.59,0:02:29.64,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,so that you can be well-liked.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.59,0:02:29.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,是非とももててくださいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.84,0:02:33.85,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,Serpens, the one that isn't Hydra,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.84,0:02:33.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして 海蛇座ならぬ蛇座のほうも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.85,0:02:36.77,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,is also a symbol of immortality, \Nthough not as much as the hydra.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.85,0:02:36.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ヒドラでこそありませんが\N不死身性の象徴ではありますからね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.15,0:02:42.40,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,After all, Serpens has a special \Ncharacteristic that you can say
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.15,0:02:42.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なにせ この蛇座というのは全天八十八星座の中でも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.40,0:02:46.03,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,is unique among all 88 \Nconstellations in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.40,0:02:46.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,唯一と言っていい\N変わった特徴を持っていますからね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.32,0:02:49.03,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,Do you know what it is, Araragi-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.32,0:02:49.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんだかご存知ですか? 阿良々木先輩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.03,0:02:50.16,Default Mid Low Cen,screen,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.78,0:02:53.95,Default - Italics,Koyomi,0,0,0,,Does Ougi-chan know what it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.78,0:02:53.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,扇ちゃんは知っているのだろうか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.20,0:02:56.20,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,I don't know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.20,0:02:56.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私は何も知りませんよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.41,0:02:59.33,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,It's what you know, Araragi-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.41,0:02:59.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あなたが知っているんです 阿良々木先輩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.58,0:03:05.09,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,In reality, you should know what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.58,0:03:05.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,御存知のはずですよ 本当は
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.34,0:03:06.96,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,See, like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.34,0:03:06.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほら こういう風に
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.96,0:03:11.43,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,Serpens is the only constellation that exists \Nsplit up into the eastern and western parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.96,0:03:11.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,蛇座は東西に分断されて存在する\Nただひとつの星座なのです
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.09,0:03:14.10,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,As a snake... It has been chopped up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.09,0:03:14.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,蛇として ぶつ切りにされている
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.10,0:03:18.31,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,This clearly shows immortality.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.10,0:03:18.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これは 見るからに不死身ですよね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.81,0:03:21.90,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,It's still alive despite its \Nbody chopped in half.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.81,0:03:21.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,身体を真っ二つにされても生きているだなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.90,0:03:23.40,Default Mid Low Cen,screen,0,0,0,,Well, Araragi-senpai, you seem to have your \Nbody chopped into half rather often as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.40,0:03:28.78,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,Actually, in the gap where it is split up, a \Ndifferent constellation has been drawn in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.40,0:03:28.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,実を言いますと 分断されたその狭間には\N別の星座が描かれているのですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.99,0:03:34.66,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,I'm sure you know of it, Araragi-senpai, \Nbut it's Ophiuchus (snake charmer).
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.99,0:03:34.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これは絶対に阿良々木先輩はご存知だと思いますが\N蛇遣い座です
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.49,0:03:38.79,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,The picture depicts the snake charmer \Nholding the upper and lower halves...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.49,0:03:38.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,蛇遣いが 蛇の上半身と下半身を
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.79,0:03:42.29,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,...of the snake's body with his left \Nand right arms, respectively.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.79,0:03:42.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,左腕右腕でそれぞれ持っているという図になるのですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.25,0:03:47.92,Default,Koyomi,0,0,0,,If I recall, that snake charmer was \NAsklepios, dubbed the sage physician?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.25,0:03:47.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,確か あの蛇遣いは医聖と呼ばれる\Nアスクレピオスなのだっけ?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.92,0:03:48.92,Default Mid Low,screen,0,0,0,,Sage physician
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.09,0:03:53.18,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,That's right. Nothing less from you, \NAraragi-senpai. You really have extensive knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.09,0:03:53.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうですね さすが阿良々木先輩\N博識でいらっしゃる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.35,0:03:57.81,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,Asklepios' medical skills were \Nhoned remarkably quickly,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.35,0:03:57.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アスクレピオスの医術の技は\Nめきめきと洗練され
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.81,0:04:01.48,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,and it got to a point where he \Ncould even resurrect the dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.81,0:04:01.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しまいには死人さえも蘇(よみがえ)らせるレベルにまで達したのです
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.31,0:04:05.06,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,However, that was going too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.31,0:04:05.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,けれど これはやり過ぎだった
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.19,0:04:07.07,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,Going too far. Against the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.19,0:04:07.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やり過ぎ ルール違反
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.69,0:04:10.40,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,I guess you could say it went \Nagainst the logic of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.69,0:04:10.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,世の理(ことわり)に反すると言いますかね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.40,0:04:12.57,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,Bringing forth anger of Hades \Nthe god of the underworld,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.40,0:04:12.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,冥王(めいおう)ハーデスの怒りを買い
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.57,0:04:17.95,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,Asklepios was struck by lightning \Nand literally sent to heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.57,0:04:17.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アスクレピオスは雷に打たれて\N文字通り天に召されたというわけです
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.20,0:04:24.71,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,Well, bringing a person back to life -- to \Nmass-produce immortals -- is quite the sin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.20,0:04:24.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まあ 人を生き返らせるというのは\N不死身を量産するというのは 結構な罪ということですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.00,0:04:29.71,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,Yotsugi Ononoki-chan is also among those \Nwho were resurrected after death, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.00,0:04:29.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,斧乃木余接ちゃんも\N死後に生き返らされた一人ではありますが
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.97,0:04:32.84,Default Mid Low,screen,0,0,0,,Tadatsuru Teori
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.30,0:04:36.47,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,All parties responsible for\N her resurrection faced retaliation...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.30,0:04:36.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,彼女を生き返らせた当事者は全員\Nそのしっぺ返しで
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.84,0:04:33.72,Default Mid Low,screen,0,0,0,,Yoduru Kagenui
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.72,0:04:34.59,Default Mid Low,screen,0,0,0,,Meme Oshino
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.59,0:04:35.47,Default Mid Low,screen,0,0,0,,Deishu Kaiki
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.10,0:04:40.35,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,...and had curses placed \Nupon their bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.10,0:04:40.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その身に呪いを受けましたからね
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.35,0:04:41.35,Default Mid Low,screen,0,0,0,,Hm? What's this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.35,0:04:42.10,Default Mid Low,screen,0,0,0,,Curses?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.27,0:04:44.52,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,If that's the case, what's \Ngoing to happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.27,0:04:44.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,となるとどうなんでしょうねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.77,0:04:51.35,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,What kind of penalty will Gaen-san pay in the \Nfuture for reviving Araragi-senpai from hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.77,0:04:51.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,阿良々木先輩を地獄から復活させた臥煙さんは\N今後一体どんな報いを受けることになるのでしょうねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.35,0:04:52.36,Default Mid Low,screen,0,0,0,,Izuko Gaen
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.53,0:04:53.74,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,Ha-hah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.53,0:04:53.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はっはー
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.99,0:04:56.87,Default,Koyomi,0,0,0,,Ougi-chan, if you're going to sit \Ndown, sit on my left side.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.99,0:04:56.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,扇ちゃん 座るなら左側に
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.87,0:04:58.87,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,Hmm? Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.87,0:04:58.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうしてです?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.66,0:05:02.04,Default,Koyomi,0,0,0,,That's Senjougahara's seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.66,0:05:02.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そこは戦場ヶ原の席だから
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.37,0:05:05.42,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,My oh my, that is not a cheap seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.37,0:05:05.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おやおや これはお安くありませんねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.42,0:05:07.17,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,Well, please don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.42,0:05:07.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まあ ご心配なく
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.17,0:05:11.55,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,I have never had any intentions of taking \Nover the throne of the main heroine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.17,0:05:11.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私はメインヒロインの座を脅(おびや)かそうというつもりは毛頭ありませんよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.55,0:05:14.63,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,I wouldn't mind striving to be a \N"little sister" character...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.55,0:05:14.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,妹キャラくらいなら目指してもいいところですが...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.68,0:05:21.27,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,But, Karen-chan aside, I wouldn't want \Nto compete against Tsukihi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.68,0:05:21.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし火憐ちゃんはともかく\N月火ちゃんとは競いたくはありませんかねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.10,0:05:24.64,Default - Italics,Koyomi,0,0,0,,She is... Her true identity is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.10,0:05:24.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,彼女は... 彼女の正体は
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.40,0:05:30.15,Default - Italics,Koyomi,0,0,0,,Tadatsuru Teori said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.40,0:05:30.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,手折正弦は言った
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.90,0:05:32.78,Default - Italics,Koyomi,0,0,0,,He told me at the bottom of hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.90,0:05:32.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,地獄の底で僕に教えてくれた
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.32,0:05:37.49,Default - Italics,Koyomi,0,0,0,,He mentioned the name of the client who \Nrequested him to exterminate me and Shinobu...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.32,0:05:37.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,彼は 僕や忍の退治を依頼したクライアントの名を...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.16,0:05:43.41,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,Araragi-senpai. What do you \Nthink is the right thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.16,0:05:43.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,阿良々木先輩 正しさってなんだと思います?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.41,0:05:44.66,Default Top,screen,0,0,0,,Oh no, you don't have to think \Ntoo seriously about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.97,0:05:48.08,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,It is difficult to be \Ndoing the right thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.97,0:05:48.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,正しいことをするというのは 難しいですからね
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.33,0:05:52.92,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,It is especially difficult to \Ndo "just the right thing."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.33,0:05:52.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,特に "正しいことだけをする" というのは\Nとても難しいです
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.71,0:05:57.64,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,If you try to do the right thing, you \Nend up also having to do attachments,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.71,0:05:57.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,正しいことをしようとすると\N付属して 間違ったこと
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.64,0:06:00.60,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,wrong things or things that are not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.64,0:06:00.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,正しくないこともしなくちゃあならなくなったりします
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.01,0:06:03.06,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,So that's why, Araragi-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.01,0:06:03.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だからですね 阿良々木先輩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.06,0:06:04.06,Default Mid Low Cen,screen,0,0,0,,To win, there is an absolute need \Nto lose somewhere along the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.27,0:06:08.81,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,As long as you are being the right self, \Nyou should not be doing the right thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.27,0:06:08.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,正しい自分である上では\N正しいことをするべきではないんですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.19,0:06:13.36,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,In the end, if a mistake always accompanies \Nyou when you try to do the right thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.19,0:06:13.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,正しいことをしようとすれば\N必ずそこに間違いが伴う
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.36,0:06:14.82,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,and if that's the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.36,0:06:14.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,というのであれば...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.69,0:06:19.07,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,In the end it all balances out to zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.69,0:06:19.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,結局差し引きゼロになってしまいますからね
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.70,0:06:23.99,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,Therefore, the way of life that Kagenui-san \Nand the Fire Sisters practice
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.70,0:06:23.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ですから 影縫さんやファイヤーシスターズが\N実践している生きざまは
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.99,0:06:26.96,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,is something they claim to be justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.99,0:06:26.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,彼女達自身は正義を名乗っていますけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.96,0:06:29.96,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,But, it is not necessarily \N"doing the right thing."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.96,0:06:29.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,決して "正しいことをしている" わけではありません
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.50,0:06:35.21,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,To stay the right selves, they \Ndo not do the right thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.50,0:06:35.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,彼女達は正しい自分であるために\N正しいことをするのではなく
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.21,0:06:36.47,Default Top,screen,0,0,0,,MISTAKES
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.38,0:06:36.76,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,but correct mistakes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.38,0:06:36.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,間違いを正す...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.72,0:06:37.72,Default Top,screen,0,0,0,,INJUSTICE
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.76,0:06:40.34,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,... and correct injustice. That is \Nthe way of life they choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.76,0:06:40.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,不正を正す...\Nそういう生き方を選んでいるのです
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.34,0:06:41.60,Default Mid Low Cen,screen,0,0,0,,EXAMINE (tadasu)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.55,0:06:41.35,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,Examine (tadasu)...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.58,0:06:44.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,糺す あるいは問い質す\Nとも言いますがね
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.35,0:06:44.22,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,...or Inquire a question (toi-tadasu), \NI guess you could say.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.60,0:06:42.60,Default Mid Low Cen,screen,0,0,0,,INQUIRE (tadasu)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.47,0:06:50.23,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,In other words, your foe's foe is not your \Nally, but by becoming a foe against evil,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.47,0:06:50.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つまり 敵の敵は味方ではありませんけれど\N悪の敵となることで
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.23,0:06:55.23,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,by becoming the antonym to evil, you \Nassign yourself justice, so to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.23,0:06:55.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悪の対義語となることで\N己に正義を任ずるということですかね
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.57,0:07:01.35,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,And I am also one that seeks the type \Nof "right" that corrects mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.57,0:07:01.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして私もまた 間違いを正すタイプの\N正しさを追い求める者です
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.16,0:07:09.67,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,It is my role to eject those \Nthat have broken the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.16,0:07:09.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ルール違反をした者に退場を命じるのが\N私の役割です
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.67,0:07:10.67,Default Mid Low,screen,0,0,0,,TO SCATTER (kakusan)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.67,0:07:10.75,Default - Italics,Koyomi,0,0,0,,Broken the rules...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.67,0:07:10.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ルール違反...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.67,0:07:11.67,Default Mid Low Cen,screen,0,0,0,,TO DISPERSE (musan)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.75,0:07:11.67,Default - Italics,Koyomi,0,0,0,,...ejection.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.75,0:07:11.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,退場
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.84,0:07:16.05,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,Araragi-senpai, the program \Nis about to end.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.84,0:07:16.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,阿良々木先輩\Nそろそろプログラムが終わります
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.38,0:07:18.17,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,It's better for you to \Nwake up now, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.38,0:07:18.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,目を覚ましたほうがいいですよ?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.88,0:07:22.85,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,You should at least continue to enjoy
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.88,0:07:22.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,恋する相手とのデートを
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.85,0:07:25.59,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,the rest of your date with the \Nperson you're in love with.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.85,0:07:25.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この後も精々楽しんできてくださいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.35,0:07:29.27,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,But, since you have the \Nchance, Araragi-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.35,0:07:29.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも 折角ですから阿良々木先輩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.27,0:07:31.86,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,Please think about the answer to \Nthe question of what you think
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.27,0:07:31.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,正しさってなんだと思うかという問いの答は
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.27,0:07:34.40,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,is the right thing when you \Nhave to kill some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.27,0:07:34.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,暇潰しに考えておいてください
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.77,0:07:38.11,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,Let's talk about it again when \NI see you in real life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.77,0:07:38.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,現実世界で会ったときに\Nそれについてお話ししましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.11,0:07:38.86,Default Mid Low,screen,0,0,0,,Yeah, I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.86,0:07:39.86,Default Mid Low,screen,0,0,0,,If I still remember when I wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.15,0:07:42.62,Default,Koyomi,0,0,0,,But really, what in the world \Nis your true identity?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.15,0:07:42.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だけどきみは本当に何者なんだい?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.91,0:07:47.58,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,That too will be discussed \Nthe next time I see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.91,0:07:47.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それも またお会いしたときにお話しさせてもらいますよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.00,0:07:51.50,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,But well, if I were to force myself to \Nsay what I can say at this moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.00,0:07:51.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まあでも 今 言える限りのことを強いて言うなら
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.33,0:07:53.29,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.33,0:07:53.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私は...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.00,0:07:56.00,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,...the principles of the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.00,0:07:56.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,宇宙の法則ですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.63,0:07:57.92,Default - Italics,Koyomi,0,0,0,,Space map...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.63,0:07:57.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,宇宙地図...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.13,0:07:59.59,Default - Italics,Koyomi,0,0,0,,...in the shape of a hand fan (ougi).
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.13,0:07:59.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,扇の形
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.92,0:08:03.55,Default - Italics,Koyomi,0,0,0,,Pitch black vacuum...\N and unbalanced galaxies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.92,0:08:03.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,真っ黒な真空に... 偏った銀河
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.80,0:08:06.10,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,Don't think about this too hard, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.80,0:08:06.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これも深く考えないでください
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.10,0:08:10.31,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,Now that you came back from hell, and returned \Nto being completely human, Araragi-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.10,0:08:10.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,地獄から蘇り\N今や完全なる人間に戻った阿良々木先輩とは
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.60,0:08:16.08,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,Surprisingly enough, I may no longer have to be \Nconcerned with you anymore... if things go well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.60,0:08:16.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,案外私は これ以上関わらずに済むかもしれませんから\Nあわよくば
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.06,0:08:17.94,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,So, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.06,0:08:17.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ですから
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.15,0:08:22.36,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,I beg of you, don't get suckered \Ninto Gaen-san's slick talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.15,0:08:22.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お願いですから 臥煙さんの口車に乗らないでくださいね
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.91,0:08:27.37,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,Concerning Kiss-shot Acerola-orion \NHeart-under-blade now in her complete form,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.91,0:08:27.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,完全体となったキスショット・アセロラオリオン・ハートアンダーブレードや
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.37,0:08:30.54,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,or Mayoi Hachikuji who has,\N after resting in peace, returned again,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.37,0:08:30.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,成仏しておきながら またもこの世に舞い戻った
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.54,0:08:33.08,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,got lost again, within this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.54,0:08:33.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,迷い戻った八九寺真宵について
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.08,0:08:36.34,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,This time, I expect, from \Nthe bottom of my heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.08,0:08:36.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今度こそ "見捨てる" という正しい判断をされることを
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.59,0:08:38.85,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,that you'll make the right \Ndecision to forsake them...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.59,0:08:38.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私は心から期待しますよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.34,0:08:41.72,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,Araragi-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.34,0:08:41.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,阿良々木先輩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.22,0:08:48.22,Default Mid Low Cen,screen,0,0,0,,I woke up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.22,0:08:49.22,Default Mid Low Cen,screen,0,0,0,,I woke up?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.48,0:08:54.10,Default,Koyomi,0,0,0,,Senjougahara....
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.48,0:08:54.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,戦場ヶ原...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.69,0:08:59.81,Default,Hitagi,0,0,0,,I'm not asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.69,0:08:59.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,寝てないわ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.44,0:09:01.65,Default,Hitagi,0,0,0,,I'm not asleep at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.44,0:09:01.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,全然寝てない
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.32,0:09:06.49,Default,Hitagi,0,0,0,,I'm not asleep at all. I was just \Nthinking with my eyes shut.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.32,0:09:06.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,全然寝てない\N目を瞑(つむ)って考え事をしていただけ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.24,0:09:10.87,Default,Hitagi,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I was actually asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.24,0:09:10.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ごめんなさい 本当は寝ていました
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.62,0:09:15.08,Default,Koyomi,0,0,0,,It's fine. I was asleep for a bit, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.62,0:09:15.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大丈夫 僕もちょっと寝ちゃってたから
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.33,0:09:18.79,Default,Hitagi,0,0,0,,I see. I guess it means \Nwe were both tired?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.33,0:09:18.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そう お互い疲れていたということかしら
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.59,0:09:25.43,Default,Hitagi,0,0,0,,I guess it was too hasty to go on a date\Nafter we only decided on it yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.59,0:09:25.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さすがに昨日の今日でデートというのは\N突貫工事過ぎたわね
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.43,0:09:30.55,Default,Koyomi,0,0,0,,So, what kind of plans did \Nyou have after this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.43,0:09:30.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,で ここから先はどういう予定になっているんだ?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.07,0:09:36.44,Default,Hitagi,0,0,0,,We're going to learn the state-of-the-art \Nscience at the adjoining science museum.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.07,0:09:36.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,併設の科学館で現代の最新鋭の科学を学ぶのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.65,0:09:39.61,Default,Hitagi,0,0,0,,After doing a tour of the science \Nmuseum, we'll have lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.65,0:09:39.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,科学館を一周したあとは 昼食よ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.61,0:09:41.78,Default,Hitagi,0,0,0,,The plan was to study during the morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.61,0:09:41.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,午前中はお勉強プランだったから
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.44,0:09:42.44,Default Top,,0,0,0,,Floor Map
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.78,0:09:44.19,Default,Hitagi,0,0,0,,so I have mainly leisurely activities \Nplanned for the afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.78,0:09:44.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,午後は遊びをメインに据えているわ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.49,0:09:47.91,Default,Hitagi,0,0,0,,We'll go out to the city by car, and \Nspend the first half bowling.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.49,0:09:47.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クルマでちょっと町まで出て\N前半はボウリング
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.91,0:09:50.49,Default,Hitagi,0,0,0,,After a bit of tea time, we'll spend \Nthe second half singing karaoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.91,0:09:50.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ティータイムを挟んで 後半はカラオケよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.49,0:09:51.37,Default,Koyomi,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.58,0:09:54.25,Default,Hitagi,0,0,0,,Araragi-kun, what's your \Nhigh score in bowling?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.58,0:09:54.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,阿良々木くん ボウリングのハイスコアは?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.46,0:09:59.04,Default,Koyomi,0,0,0,,Well, I'm a novice at bowling altogether, \Nlike I don't think I've ever played before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.46,0:09:59.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや ボウリング自体初心者で\Nたぶんやったことないと思うんだけど
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.34,0:10:01.66,Default,Hitagi,0,0,0,,Got it. There will be a \Npenalty on the loser.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.34,0:10:01.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わかった 負けたら罰ゲームね
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.59,0:10:05.92,Default,Koyomi,0,0,0,,Don't set up a penalty after it came \Nto light that I'm a novice!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.59,0:10:05.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,僕が初心者と判明してから罰ゲームを設定するな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.92,0:10:10.02,Default,Hitagi,0,0,0,,The loser must swear absolute \Nobedience to the winner.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.92,0:10:10.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,敗者は勝者の命令に絶対服従
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.02,0:10:11.47,Default,Koyomi,0,0,0,,That's a really harsh penalty!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.02,0:10:11.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,罰ゲームが重いよ!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.14,0:10:50.30,Default,Hitagi,0,0,0,,Dammit... To think that Araragi-kun \Nwould actually lie to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.14,0:10:50.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おのれ... まさか阿良々木くんが私に嘘をつくなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.59,0:10:52.51,Default,Hitagi,0,0,0,,You're not a novice at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.59,0:10:52.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,全然初心者じゃないじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.51,0:10:53.89,KOYOKOYO,screen,0,0,0,,KOYOKOYO
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.51,0:10:53.89,HITAGI,screen,0,0,0,,HITAGI
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.35,0:10:57.64,Default - Italics,Koyomi,0,0,0,,From about the first frame \Ntill about the fifth frame,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.35,0:10:57.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,第一フレームから第五フレームあたりまでは
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.40,0:11:00.77,HITAGI,screen,0,0,0,,HITAGI
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.40,0:11:00.77,KOYOKOYO,screen,0,0,0,,KOYOKOYO
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.36,0:11:03.02,Default - Italics,Koyomi,0,0,0,,she showed amazing skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.36,0:11:03.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見事な腕前だった
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.02,0:11:04.40,HITAGI,screen,0,0,0,,HITAGI
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.02,0:11:04.40,KOYOKOYO,screen,0,0,0,,KOYOKOYO
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.19,0:11:09.49,Default - Italics,Koyomi,0,0,0,,However, starting at the sixth \Nframe, her playing...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.19,0:11:09.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし第六フレーム以降 彼女のプレイは
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.03,0:11:07.40,HITAGI,screen,0,0,0,,HITAGI
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.03,0:11:07.40,KOYOKOYO,screen,0,0,0,,KOYOKOYO
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.86,0:11:10.28,Limits,screen,0,0,0,,LIMITS OF ACTIVITY
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.28,0:11:11.28,HITAGI,screen,0,0,0,,HITAGI
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.28,0:11:11.28,KOYOKOYO,screen,0,0,0,,KOYOKOYO
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.28,0:11:12.91,Default - Italics,Koyomi,0,0,0,,...suddenly changed.\N Completely changed...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.28,0:11:12.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一転した 一変した
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.04,0:11:16.04,Default - Italics,Koyomi,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.04,0:11:18.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そう 戦場ヶ原は疲れたのである
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.04,0:11:18.41,Default - Italics,Koyomi,0,0,0,,Senjougahara was exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.42,0:11:20.92,Default - Italics,Koyomi,0,0,0,,Seems that her arm went numb.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.42,0:11:20.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,腕が痺(しび)れたらしい
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.92,0:11:22.42,KOYOKOYO,screen,0,0,0,,KOYOKOYO
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.92,0:11:22.42,HITAGIBLUE,screen,0,0,0,,HITAGI
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.67,0:11:26.06,Default,Hitagi,0,0,0,,Fine. I will admit defeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.67,0:11:26.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいわ 負けを認めるわよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.66,0:11:28.67,Default,Hitagi,0,0,0,,You can order me to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.66,0:11:28.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんでも命令するがいいわ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.30,0:11:32.77,Default,Hitagi,0,0,0,,So, I wonder what kind of lewd \Nrequest will you make of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.30,0:11:32.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さあ どんなエッチな要求をしてくれるのかしら?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.76,0:11:36.02,Default,Hitagi,0,0,0,,My anticipation only heightens.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.76,0:11:36.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,期待は高まるばかりだわ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.02,0:11:39.14,Default,Koyomi,0,0,0,,Just for reference, if you \Nhad won, Senjougahara,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.02,0:11:39.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ちなみに戦場ヶ原が勝っていた場合は
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.14,0:11:40.85,Default,Koyomi,0,0,0,,what kind of request were \Nyou going to make?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.14,0:11:40.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どんな要求をするつもりだったのか
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.60,0:11:44.98,Default,Hitagi,0,0,0,,I was going to make a lewd \Nrequest, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.60,0:11:44.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当然 エロい要求をするつもりだったわよ!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.07,0:11:52.49,Default - Italics,Koyomi,0,0,0,,I struck a deal with something like, "Then \Nlet's walk arm-in-arm until our tea time."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.07,0:11:52.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃあティータイムまで\N腕を組んで歩こうという辺りで手を打った
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.08,0:12:00.29,Default,Hitagi,0,0,0,,Hmm... To think that you were having an adventure of \Nthat sort on the actual day of the entrance exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.08,0:12:00.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふうん... まさか受験日当日に\Nそんなアドベンチャーを繰り広げていたとは
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.29,0:12:03.25,Default,Hitagi,0,0,0,,It's unexpected, but it's so \Nfitting for you, Araragi-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.29,0:12:03.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,意外と言うか\N阿良々木くんらしいと言うか...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.25,0:12:05.42,Default,Hitagi,0,0,0,,Though, I have to ask, what in \Nthe world were you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.25,0:12:05.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何をやっているんだと言うか
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.21,0:12:10.92,Default,Hitagi,0,0,0,,it's unclear exactly what Gaen-san \Nis fighting against...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.21,0:12:10.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,臥煙さんが何と戦っているのかは定かではないけれども...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.92,0:12:15.42,Default,Hitagi,0,0,0,,But perhaps you, Araragi-kun, are \Nthe opponent of that battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.92,0:12:15.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ひょっとしたら それは\N阿良々木くんを相手に戦っているのかもしれないわよね
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.14,0:12:20.43,Default,Hitagi,0,0,0,,No, it's more of a hunch than any meaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.14,0:12:20.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いえ 意味と言うよりは直感なんだけれども
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.43,0:12:23.65,Default,Hitagi,0,0,0,,Compared to your stance, Araragi-kun, where you \Ncan only see what is right in front of your eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.43,0:12:23.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,目の前のことしか見えない阿良々木くんの姿勢とは
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.65,0:12:27.94,Default,Hitagi,0,0,0,,that macroscopic stance Gaen-san takes would \Nclash no matter how you look at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.65,0:12:27.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうしたって臥煙さんの巨視的なスタンスは\N対立しそうだなって
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.15,0:12:33.24,Default,Hitagi,0,0,0,,Clash... or oppose, if you want \Na slightly harsher term.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.15,0:12:33.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,対立 もう少し厳しく言うならば\N敵対 かしら
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.78,0:12:39.83,Default,Hitagi,0,0,0,,We'll duke it out for two hours, and \Nthe one who loses in total points...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.78,0:12:39.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,二時間対決して\N総合得点で負けたほうは勝ったほうに
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.83,0:12:40.83,Default Top,screen,0,0,0,,Karaoke\N{\c&H3941EA&}Red-{\c&HDDE1DE&}White {\c&H48E3DF&}Song Battle
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.96,0:12:42.58,Default,Hitagi,0,0,0,,...swears absolute obedience \Nto the winner.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.96,0:12:42.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,絶対服従ね
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.58,0:12:43.58,Song Name,screen,0,0,0,,Song: "Futakotome"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.58,0:12:43.58,Song Seting,screen,0,0,0,,Setting: Original Key
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.42,0:12:48.30,Default,Hitagi,0,0,0,,I'll go first. You listen well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.42,0:12:48.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,先攻私 聞くがいいわ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.09,0:12:52.17,DefaultTopLeft,screen,0,0,0,,Challenger: Hitagi-san                                            Song: Futakotome\NScore: 82.107%
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.09,0:12:52.17,Default Bot Left Small,screen,0,0,0,,Analysis: You have very high singing skills, \Nbut emotional expression seems slightly weak.\N It will be better if you add\N more intonation to your singing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.17,0:12:53.60,Default,Hitagi,0,0,0,,An 82...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.17,0:12:53.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,82点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.60,0:12:54.35,Default,Hitagi,0,0,0,,Lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.60,0:12:54.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,嘘
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.55,0:12:59.85,Default,Hitagi,0,0,0,,82 percent is a failing score. This is the \Nfirst time I've ever scored in the low eighties.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.55,0:12:59.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,82点って 赤点じゃない\N生まれて初めて八十点台前半を取ったわ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.14,0:13:02.97,Default - Italics,Koyomi,0,0,0,,What kind of test is it if 82 \Npercent is a failing score?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.14,0:13:02.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,82点が赤点って どんなテストだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.23,0:13:07.73,Default,Hitagi,0,0,0,,Araragi-kun, you spent the majority of your \Nhigh school career feeling like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.23,0:13:07.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,阿良々木くんは\N高校生活の大半をこんな気分で過ごしてきたの...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.73,0:13:09.86,Default,Hitagi,0,0,0,,I was not able to understand it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.73,0:13:09.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,理解してあげられてなかったわ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.86,0:13:12.24,Default,Hitagi,0,0,0,,I was supposed to be a lot kinder to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.86,0:13:12.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もっと優しくしてあげなきゃいけなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.24,0:13:15.87,Default,Hitagi,0,0,0,,What kind of horrible things have \NI been saying to Araragi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.24,0:13:15.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私はなんて酷いことを\N阿良々木くんに言ってきたんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.87,0:13:17.74,Default - Italics,Koyomi,0,0,0,,You're saying those horrible \Nthings right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.87,0:13:17.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,酷いことは今言ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.74,0:13:18.74,Song Name,screen,0,0,0,,Song: chocolate
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.74,0:13:18.74,Song Seting,screen,0,0,0,,Setting: original key
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.25,0:13:24.62,DefaultTopLeft,screen,0,0,0,,Challenger: Koyokoyo-san                   Song: chocolate insomnia\NScore: 82.438%
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.25,0:13:24.62,Default Bot Left Small,screen,0,0,0,,Analysis: All elements are coming together\N at a very high level. Keep it up,\N and 100% is not just a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.00,0:13:31.01,Default Top,screen,0,0,0,,Loser - Red 819           RESULTS       Winner - White 822
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.26,0:13:34.01,Default - Italics,Koyomi,0,0,0,,And once again, I was the winner.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.26,0:13:34.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして勝ったのはまたも僕だった
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.30,0:13:39.89,Default,Hitagi,0,0,0,,Impossible... To think that I would lose \Nagainst Araragi-kun twice in one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.30,0:13:39.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,馬鹿な... この私が阿良々木くんに\N一日のうちに二度も負けるだなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.64,0:13:43.32,Default,Hitagi,0,0,0,,Now, feel free to give \Nme any order you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.64,0:13:43.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さあ 何でも命令するがいいわ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.64,0:13:47.97,Default,Hitagi,0,0,0,,How about you carry me to \Nour car like a princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.64,0:13:47.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,駐車場までお姫さま抱っこっていうのはどうかしら?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.98,0:13:51.65,Default,Hitagi,0,0,0,,I'll kill you if you say I'm heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.98,0:13:51.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,重いって言ったら殺すからね
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.36,0:13:56.03,Default,Hitagi,0,0,0,,Nothing less from you, Araragi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.36,0:13:56.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さすが阿良々木くん
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.03,0:13:59.24,Default,Hitagi,0,0,0,,It shows that you're used to cradling young \Ngirls in your arms in everyday life.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.03,0:13:59.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,普段から幼女を抱っこし慣れているだけのことはあるわね
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.24,0:13:59.99,Default Mid Low Cen,screen,0,0,0,,That particular expression \Nleads to misunderstandings.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.99,0:14:00.74,Default Mid Low Cen,screen,0,0,0,,I'd like you to stop that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.74,0:14:02.24,Default Top,,0,0,0,,Hourly Parking\N Entrance 50m ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.41,0:14:04.50,Default,Hitagi,0,0,0,,Whew. That was embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.41,0:14:04.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふう 恥ずかしかった
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.79,0:14:07.00,Default,Hitagi,0,0,0,,I just saw hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.79,0:14:07.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,地獄を見たわ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.25,0:14:08.83,Default - Italics,Koyomi,0,0,0,,You'd go that far?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.25,0:14:08.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そこまで言うか
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.25,0:14:10.21,Default Top,screen,0,0,0,,MORE HELLISH THAN HELL
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.89,0:14:20.18,Default,Koyomi,0,0,0,,Senjougahara....
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.89,0:14:20.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,戦場ヶ原...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.47,0:14:21.97,Default,Koyomi,0,0,0,,I have something important to talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.47,0:14:21.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大事な話があるんだが
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.26,0:14:24.48,Default,Hitagi,0,0,0,,If it's a request to get \Nmarried, I'm okay with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.26,0:14:24.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,結婚の申し込みならＯＫよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.48,0:14:26.98,Default,Koyomi,0,0,0,,No, it's not that important a topic.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.48,0:14:26.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや そこまで大事な話じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.48,0:14:29.06,Default,Koyomi,0,0,0,,And that was way too instant a reply.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.48,0:14:29.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そしてふたつ返事過ぎる
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.23,0:14:30.23,Default Top,screen,0,0,0,,IT TURNED INTO A MARRIAGE PROPOSAL
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.44,0:14:34.94,Default,Koyomi,0,0,0,,Actually, it's about a gift in return for the \Nchocolate I received for Valentine's Day...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.44,0:14:34.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,実は バレンタインデーに頂いた\Nチョコレートのお返しの件なんだが
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.94,0:14:36.45,Default,Koyomi,0,0,0,,I haven't been able to get one ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.94,0:14:36.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,用意できてないんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.70,0:14:39.53,Default,Koyomi,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I didn't have \Ntime to get one ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.70,0:14:39.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ごめんなさい 用意する時間がなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.53,0:14:41.99,Default,Koyomi,0,0,0,,In thinking of what to get, \NI thought way too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.53,0:14:41.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,考えているうちに考え過ぎてしまって
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.08,0:14:42.66,Default Top,screen,0,0,0,,HONEST MAN
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.91,0:14:45.58,Default,Koyomi,0,0,0,,So, can you wait two or three more days?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.91,0:14:45.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なので二 三日待ってはもらえないだろうか
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.66,0:14:46.25,Default Top,screen,0,0,0,,THINKING TOO MUCH
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.41,0:14:49.29,Default,Koyomi,0,0,0,,Of course, I'll tack on the interest \Naccrued during that period.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.41,0:14:49.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もちろん その分の利息は上乗せするから
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.29,0:14:52.21,Default,Hitagi,0,0,0,,What, you were worried about such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.29,0:14:52.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんだ そんなことを気に病んでいたの
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.46,0:14:55.42,Default,Hitagi,0,0,0,,It was enough for me that you went on \Na date with me the whole day today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.46,0:14:55.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今日一日 デートしてくれただけでも十分よ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.09,0:14:59.89,Default,Hitagi,0,0,0,,It's fine for you to just give me \Nsomething when you feel like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.09,0:14:59.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,気が向いたら何かくれるくらいでいいわよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.89,0:15:03.43,Default,Hitagi,0,0,0,,It wasn't like I made that chocolate \Nexpecting to receive something in return.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.89,0:15:03.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私はお返しを期待してチョコレートを作ったわけではないわ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.31,0:15:13.40,Default,Hitagi,0,0,0,,Araragi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.31,0:15:13.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,阿良々木くん
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.40,0:15:14.78,Default,Hitagi,0,0,0,,It's unforgivable.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.40,0:15:14.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,許せないわね
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.03,0:15:15.53,Default,Koyomi,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.53,0:15:19.78,Default,Hitagi,0,0,0,,I can't hardly believe that, on White Day,\N one of the three big events of the year for couples,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.53,0:15:19.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あろうことか恋人達の三大イベントのひとつであるホワイトデーに
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.78,0:15:22.53,Default,Hitagi,0,0,0,,you don't have anything \Nprepared for your lover?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.78,0:15:22.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ラバーに対して何も用意していないだなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.87,0:15:25.66,Default,Hitagi,0,0,0,,I have to doubt that you have \Nany affection towards me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.87,0:15:25.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私に対する愛情を疑わざるを得ないわ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.66,0:15:27.16,Default,Koyomi,0,0,0,,Eh? Ehh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.96,0:15:33.84,Default,Hitagi,0,0,0,,All day today, I was wondering exactly what \Nkind of surprise Araragi-kun had prepared for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.96,0:15:33.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今日一日 阿良々木くんはいったいどんなサプライズを用意してくれているんだろうと
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.84,0:15:37.85,Default,Hitagi,0,0,0,,My heart was racing, and I was so excited... \NBut you didn't have anything ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.84,0:15:37.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どきどきはらはらわくわくしていたのに\N何の準備もなかっただなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.26,0:15:40.09,Default,Hitagi,0,0,0,,What a sidestep that was!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.26,0:15:40.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,肩透かしもいいところよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.30,0:15:44.93,Default,Hitagi,0,0,0,,I had assumed that you would get me a \Ncruiser or something as a present.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.30,0:15:44.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,てっきり クルーザーの一台くらい\Nプレゼントしてくれるのかと思っていたのに
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.64,0:15:48.52,Default,Koyomi,0,0,0,,I-Isn't that expectation a bit too \Nmega-sized, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.64,0:15:48.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そ それは期待がメガサイズ過ぎないかい?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.73,0:15:52.14,Default,Hitagi,0,0,0,,Oh, brother. I wonder if I \Nshould just kill myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.73,0:15:52.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あーあ 自殺しよっかなー
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.40,0:15:56.40,Default,Koyomi,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry. That's why I'm apologizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.40,0:15:56.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ご ごめん だから謝ってるじゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.78,0:15:59.53,Default,Koyomi,0,0,0,,Please don't commit suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.78,0:15:59.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自殺はしないでください
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.28,0:16:03.20,Default,Koyomi,0,0,0,,T-Then, what can I do for \Nyou to forgive me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.28,0:16:03.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃ じゃあ どうすれば許してくれる?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.20,0:16:06.29,Default,Koyomi,0,0,0,,I can't get you a cruiser, but \NI'll do whatever I can-
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.20,0:16:06.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クルーザーは用意できないけれど\Nできる限りのことなら
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.45,0:16:08.91,Default,Hitagi,0,0,0,,Did you just say you'll \Ndo whatever you can?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.45,0:16:08.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,できる限りのことをするって言った? 今
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.87,0:16:13.42,Default,Hitagi,0,0,0,,Did you say absolute obedience?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.87,0:16:13.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,絶対服従って言った?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.79,0:16:16.31,Default,Koyomi,0,0,0,,N-No, I didn't say that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.79,0:16:16.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,い いえ 言ってませんけれど...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.09,0:16:22.64,Default,Koyomi,0,0,0,,I did, I did! Indeed, I did say "absolute \Nobedience" with these lips!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.09,0:16:22.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,言いました 言いました 絶対服従と\Nまさにこの口で言いました
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.68,0:16:28.39,Default,Hitagi,0,0,0,,I see. Nothing less from you, \NAraragi-kun. Such a generous heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.68,0:16:28.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そう さすが阿良々木くん\Nその度量の広さ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.39,0:16:29.93,Default,Hitagi,0,0,0,,You really are the man \NI fell in love with.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.39,0:16:29.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私が惚れた男ね
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.39,0:16:31.56,Default,Hitagi,0,0,0,,I've fallen in love with you over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.39,0:16:31.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,惚れ直したわ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.60,0:16:35.06,Default,Hitagi,0,0,0,,You don't know what I'm \Ngoing to request of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.60,0:16:38.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何を要求されるかもわからないのに\N一生 私のお願いに絶対服従してくれるだなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.06,0:16:38.32,Default,Hitagi,0,0,0,,but you're willing to be absolutely obedient \Nto my requests for the rest of your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.32,0:16:39.32,Default,Koyomi,0,0,0,,The rest of my life!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.32,0:16:39.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一生!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.57,0:16:43.99,Default,Koyomi,0,0,0,,S-Sure. The rest of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.57,0:16:43.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お おう 一生だな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.41,0:16:47.70,Default,Koyomi,0,0,0,,I got it. What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.41,0:16:47.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わかった 僕は何をすればいいんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.70,0:16:50.04,Default,Hitagi,0,0,0,,Call my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.70,0:16:50.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,名前で呼んで
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.33,0:16:54.96,Default,Hitagi,0,0,0,,Call me... by my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.33,0:16:54.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私のこと 名前で
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.21,0:16:55.96,Default,Koyomi,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.38,0:16:58.84,Default,Koyomi,0,0,0,,I do call you. "Senjougahara."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.38,0:16:58.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,呼んでるじゃん 戦場ヶ原って
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.63,0:17:03.84,Default,Hitagi,0,0,0,,Not that. My first name, \Nwith no honorifics.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.63,0:17:03.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃなくて 下の名前で 呼び捨てに
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.01,0:17:10.85,Default - Italics,Koyomi,0,0,0,,So that's why she tried to set up a \Npenalty for bowling and karaoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.01,0:17:10.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だからボウリングやカラオケで\N罰ゲームを設けようとしていたのか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.81,0:17:16.36,Default - Italics,Koyomi,0,0,0,,If it wasn't for an opportunity like this, it may \Nhave been something I'd have never been able to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.81,0:17:16.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんなきっかけでもなければ\N言えないことだったかもしれない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.19,0:17:19.53,Default - Italics,Koyomi,0,0,0,,Absolute obedience for \Nthe rest of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.19,0:17:19.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一生 絶対服従
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.28,0:17:22.86,Default - Italics,Koyomi,0,0,0,,Calling her by that name for \Nthe rest of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.28,0:17:22.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一生 その名を呼び続ける
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.66,0:17:26.62,Default,Koyomi,0,0,0,,...Hitagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.66,0:17:26.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ひたぎ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.70,0:17:31.70,Default,Hitagi,0,0,0,,Thank you... Koyomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.70,0:17:31.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ありがとう 暦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.96,0:17:39.96,Default Top,screen,0,0,0,,ARARAGI
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.96,0:17:43.71,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,Hello, Araragi-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.96,0:17:43.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やあ 阿良々木先輩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.13,0:17:45.88,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,I've been waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.13,0:17:45.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お待ちしておりましたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.88,0:17:47.47,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,I've gotten tired of waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.88,0:17:47.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,待ちくたびれました
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.47,0:17:49.34,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,I got exhausted just by waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.47,0:17:49.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,待つだけでくたびれました
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.55,0:17:51.55,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.55,0:17:51.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いかがでした?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.76,0:17:55.35,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,Did you enjoy your last date \Nwith Senjougahara-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.76,0:17:55.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,戦場ヶ原先輩との\N最後のデートは楽しめましたか?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.60,0:18:00.19,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,At the least, I was being considerate and \Navoided butting in over on the physical world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.60,0:18:00.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一応気を遣って\N現実世界での割り込みは控えておいたんですけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.44,0:18:02.69,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,I'd like you to be appreciative of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.44,0:18:02.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,感謝していただきたいものですねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.86,0:18:04.19,Default,Koyomi,0,0,0,,I will be appreciative.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.86,0:18:04.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,感謝はする
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.19,0:18:07.57,Default,Koyomi,0,0,0,,But, how you said "the last date" \Ncreates misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.19,0:18:07.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただ 最後のデートっていう言いかたは\N誤解を招くな
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.86,0:18:10.95,Default,Koyomi,0,0,0,,It was merely the last date \Nof my high school life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.86,0:18:10.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あくまでも 高校生活\N最後のデートだ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.95,0:18:17.83,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,So is it? Yes, that would be nice if it is... \NIt'd be nice if the two of you had a future.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.95,0:18:17.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,です か ええ だったらいいですよねえ\Nお二人に 未来があればいいですよねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.42,0:18:23.88,Default,Koyomi,0,0,0,,Ougi-chan. Did you try to exterminate me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.42,0:18:23.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,扇ちゃん きみは 僕を退治しようとしたの?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.88,0:18:26.34,Default,Koyomi,0,0,0,,You asked a specialist to do such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.88,0:18:26.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんなことを 専門家に依頼したの?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.51,0:18:29.97,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,Oh, you heard from someone... \Nof such false rumors?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.51,0:18:29.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おや 誰かから聞きましたか? そんなデマを
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.14,0:18:33.89,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,But still, that is a sad false alarm...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.14,0:18:33.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかしそれは悲しい誤報ですね
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.31,0:18:36.56,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,I would like an explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.31,0:18:36.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,釈明させて欲しいところです
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.56,0:18:41.10,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,There is no way I would do anything \Nto harm you, Araragi-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.56,0:18:41.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私が阿良々木先輩を\N害するようなことをするわけがないじゃありませんか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.40,0:18:42.61,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,That's why I told you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.40,0:18:42.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから言ったでしょう?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.86,0:18:45.40,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,That I am expecting you, Araragi-senpai, \Nto make the right decision...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.86,0:18:45.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,阿良々木先輩が正しい判断をして
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.40,0:18:49.86,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,...and withdraw, instead of getting \Nsuckered into Gaen-san's slick talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.40,0:18:49.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,臥煙さんの口車に乗ることなく\N退(ひ)いてくれることを期待します と
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.74,0:18:51.99,Default,Koyomi,0,0,0,,Did you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.74,0:18:51.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,言ったっけな
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.99,0:18:52.49,Default Mid Low Cen,screen,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.49,0:18:53.49,Default Mid Low Cen,screen,0,0,0,,If she is saying she said \Nit, she probably said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.66,0:18:58.79,Default,Koyomi,0,0,0,,But, it's nonexistent. The choice of forsaking \NShinobu and Hachikuji is something I don't have.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.66,0:18:58.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だけど ないぜ\N忍や八九寺のことを見捨てるなんて選択肢は 僕には
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.75,0:19:03.13,Default,Koyomi,0,0,0,,There is no choice. I have no \Nsurplus within my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.75,0:19:03.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,選択の余地はない\N僕の心に余りはない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.75,0:19:08.17,Default,Koyomi,0,0,0,,I don't know what the right thing is, but \NI do know what path I should take.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.75,0:19:08.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,正しさが何かなんてわからないけれど\N自分の選ぶべき道はわかっている
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.17,0:19:11.43,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,I wish you wouldn't hurry to \Nconclusions like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.17,0:19:11.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そう結論を急がないで欲しいものですけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.68,0:19:15.63,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,But well, that's fine. I tried to ask you \Nbecause I had nothing left to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.68,0:19:15.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でもまあ そうですね 私としても\N駄目元で訊いてみただけです
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.72,0:19:18.14,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,That said, it's disappointing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.72,0:19:18.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,とは言え残念です
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.06,0:19:23.78,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,For me personally, I'd like to see you, \NAraragi-senpai, retire voluntarily right about now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.06,0:19:23.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私としては 阿良々木先輩には\Nここらでご勇退願いたいんですけれどね
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.48,0:19:27.94,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,But egging you on to do so too much \Nwould be going beyond my bounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.48,0:19:27.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あまりそれを促すのも\N領分を出てしまいますか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.28,0:19:30.03,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,Hey, Araragi-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.28,0:19:30.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ねえ 阿良々木先輩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.02,0:19:36.62,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,Let me correct one thing that you may \Nhave a misunderstanding about.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.02,0:19:36.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ひとつ あなたが勘違いされているかもしれないことを\N訂正させてくださいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.62,0:19:39.52,Default,Koyomi,0,0,0,,Misunderstanding? What is \Nthe misunderstanding?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.62,0:19:39.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勘違い? 勘違いって... 何?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.83,0:19:44.41,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,I am not the "darkness."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.83,0:19:44.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私は "くらやみ" ではありませんよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.09,0:19:48.68,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,By the way, Araragi-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.09,0:19:48.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ところで阿良々木先輩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.34,0:19:53.34,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,Araragi-senpai, you've fallen to \Nhell, and you've gone on a date,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.34,0:19:53.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,阿良々木先輩には 地獄に落ち\Nデートもして
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.34,0:19:56.17,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,so you may have nothing you look \Nback on with regret anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.34,0:19:56.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう思い残すことはないかもしれませんけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.60,0:20:01.55,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,But I currently have one thing that I \Nlook back on with regret in this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.60,0:20:01.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私には現在 ひとつ\Nこの町で思い残していることがありましてね
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.28,0:20:04.06,Default,Koyomi,0,0,0,,Something you look back on with regret?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.28,0:20:04.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,思い残していること?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.06,0:20:07.19,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,Something you wouldn't\N mind dying to achieve...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.06,0:20:07.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それをやり遂げるためなら死んでもいいし
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.19,0:20:11.85,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,Once you achieved this, you wouldn't mind if you died.\N Do you have such a goal, Araragi-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.19,0:20:11.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それをやり遂げたら死んでもいいという目標が\N阿良々木先輩にはありますか?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.03,0:20:16.70,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,I have one. I have just one more.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.03,0:20:16.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私にはあるのです\Nあとひとつだけ あるのです
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.70,0:20:20.79,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,That's why I have to do it even if I \Nhave to put everything else aside.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.70,0:20:20.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから何をおいても\Nそれをしなければならないのですけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.38,0:20:27.39,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,That is why if Izuko Gaen, the leader of the \Nspecialists, were to place a trap, it would be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.38,0:20:27.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だからこそ 専門家の元締め\N臥煙伊豆湖が罠を張るとすれば そこなのでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.36,0:20:30.42,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,Yes, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.36,0:20:30.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ええ わかっています
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.42,0:20:33.55,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,I know, but I still have \Nto fall for that trap...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.42,0:20:33.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わかっていても\Nその罠には引っかかるしかない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.80,0:20:37.05,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,I have to resign myself to \Nsuffer that counterattack.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.80,0:20:37.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その反撃を\N私は甘んじて受けるしかない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.10,0:20:44.14,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,In other words, starting right now, I am going to \Nfight the big sister that knows everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.10,0:20:46.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つまり 私はこれから 正面切って誤魔化しなく\N何でも知ってるおねーさんと戦うことになるのですけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.14,0:20:46.47,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,with a frontal assault,\N with no fudging around...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.41,0:20:51.98,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,Araragi-senpai, in this fight, \Ncan you be on my side?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.41,0:20:51.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,阿良々木先輩 そのときは\N私の味方をしてくれませんか?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.71,0:20:58.50,Default,Ougi,0,0,0,,Please, help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.71,0:20:58.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私を助けてください
